# 🥛 Nestlé Product Showcase Website

A simple responsive product showcase website built using **HTML** and **CSS** as part of my **Full Stack Development Journey - Day 1**.

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is a static product showcase webpage inspired by Nestlé products. It demonstrates the fundamentals of HTML and CSS, including layouts, styling, hover effects, and responsive card designs.

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 Gradient background
- 🖼️ Hero banner image
- 🥛 Dairy Products section
- 🛒 Grocery Products section
- 🍜 Packaged Foods section
- ✨ Hover animations on product cards
- 🖱️ Interactive "Order Now" buttons
- 📱 Clean and simple UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3

